    <item>
      <title>拍卖需求疲软，长期国债收益率继续上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/global-bonds-gain-ahead-of-us-labor-data-30-year-bond-auction</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国劳动力市场数据缓解了人们对经济的一些忧虑，美国国债保持下跌，促使交易员进一步降低对今年大幅降息的预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/global-bonds-gain-ahead-of-us-labor-data-30-year-bond-auction</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 09:23:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰天然气供应面临风险，欧洲天然气需求将跃升至 2024 年新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/european-gas-steadies-as-russian-transit-continues-amid-fighting</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于担心俄罗斯燃料穿越乌克兰可能中断，欧洲天然气价格连续第三天上涨，收于自 12 月以来的最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/european-gas-steadies-as-russian-transit-continues-amid-fighting</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 06:41:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
